:param columnSource1: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.sources.ColumnSource<ThreeColumnTupleSourceFactory.COLUMN_SOURCE_1_TYPE>) - The first column source
:param columnSource2: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.sources.ColumnSource<ThreeColumnTupleSourceFactory.COLUMN_SOURCE_2_TYPE>) - The second column source
:param columnSource3: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.sources.ColumnSource<ThreeColumnTupleSourceFactory.COLUMN_SOURCE_3_TYPE>) - The third column source
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.tuples.TupleSource<ThreeColumnTupleSourceFactory.TUPLE_TYPE>) The new tuple factory
